Package: CAST
Type: Package
Title: Caret Applications for Spatio-Temporal models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hanna Meyer
Maintainer: Hanna Meyer <hanna.meyer@geo.uni-marburg.de>
Description: The package includes functionality to run caret with spatial or spatio-temporal data.The package includes the functions published in Meyer, H., Reudenbach, C., Hengl, T., Katurji, M., Nauss, T.: Forward feature selection and target-oriented validation to improve performances of spatio-temporal machine learning applications. In prep for subission to Environmental Modelling and Software
